; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/kaggle-config.md

% kaggle-config, common

# View current configuration values
kaggle config view

# Set a configuration value
kaggle config set <__n___name_> <configuration_parameter> <__v___value_> <parameter_value>

# Clear a configuration value
kaggle config unset <__n___name_> <configuration_parameter>
